00:36:10.150 --> 00:36:13.380
You know, Marty is a pretty big
guy so I think it's nice to work

00:36:13.380 --> 00:36:16.390
in a pretty secure office where
we feel like nobody is going

00:36:16.390 --> 00:36:17.730
to easily come in at least--

00:36:17.730 --> 00:36:19.030
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:36:19.030 --> 00:36:20.330
&gt;&gt; Joby Warrick: --
and do harm to us.

00:36:20.330 --> 00:36:21.630
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:36:21.630 --> 00:36:22.930
&gt;&gt; Joby Warrick: My-- The one thing
