optimistic but I always assume that,

00:36:27.550 --> 00:36:29.980
hey, they like publicity
in some bizarre way,

00:36:29.980 --> 00:36:32.810
and secondly there is many more
important attractive targets

00:36:32.810 --> 00:36:35.280
than a journalist from
the Washington Post.

00:36:35.280 --> 00:36:38.370
So I do-- very, very careful when
I'm going to travel to the region--

00:36:38.370 --> 00:36:39.670
&gt;&gt; Yeah.

00:36:39.670 --> 00:36:40.970
&gt;&gt; Joby Warrick: -- and otherwise,
I just try to keep my eyes open

00:36:40.970 --> 00:36:45.270 position:56%
and then do take sort of a casual
review of the line of people waiting

00:36:45.270 --> 00:36:47.540
