sure nobody is carrying anything

00:36:47.540 --> 00:36:48.840
that looks--

00:36:48.840 --> 00:36:50.140
&gt;&gt; Yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:36:50.140 --> 00:36:51.440
&gt;&gt; Joby Warrick: -- that
