a chance to share their knowledge

00:38:54.480 --> 00:38:57.490
and to tell stories that were so
meaningful and important to them.

00:38:57.490 --> 00:39:00.630
And because, I guess one
of my gifts as a journalist

00:39:00.630 --> 00:39:03.570
