that I'm approachable

00:39:03.570 --> 00:39:06.210
and I don't have an agenda
and I just want to know

00:39:06.210 --> 00:39:07.710
and I think I come across that way.

00:39:07.710 --> 00:39:11.320
And if you just really want
to know the facts, you know,

00:39:11.320 --> 00:39:13.990
people can be surprisingly
cooperative in that regard.

00:39:13.990 --> 00:39:15.540
So I think I just gotten
lucky there.

00:39:15.540 --> 00:39:16.840
But--

00:39:16.840 --> 00:39:18.140
&gt;&gt; Well, thank you very much.

00:39:18.140 --> 00:39:19.440
