00:39:51.870 --> 00:39:53.170
It's like--

00:39:53.170 --> 00:39:54.750
&gt;&gt; Yeah, it helps that the
king of Jordan is cooperating.

00:39:54.750 --> 00:39:56.340
&gt;&gt; Joby Warrick: He kind of
