00:40:04.140 --> 00:40:05.440
&gt;&gt; Joby Warrick: Thank you.

00:40:05.440 --> 00:40:06.740
&gt;&gt; It's astounding.

00:40:06.740 --> 00:40:08.040
&gt;&gt; Joby Warrick: How are we doing?

